Segment: word segments input text (either English or Chinese; see demo)

phone: translate numeric input from a mobile telephone into alphabetic equivalent
phone1: older/longer test version of phone

markup: Segments text by language (i.e. natural language, genre, style or
       whatever text each PPM model has been trained on)
       - uses sentinel symbols followed by model numbers

markup1: uses special model sentinel numbers instead

segment: Word segmentation (English, Chinese, whatever) 

encode/Tmarkup: Generate text markup for encode/decoder
encode/Tstats: Analyze marked up text generated by Tmarkup
encode/Tencode: Encode text file using markup generated by Tmarkup
encode/Tdecode: Decode text file encoded by Tencode
